PrecisOrder fixing MONDAY, NOVEMBER 1, 1999, as the day upon which a number of amendments to the Canadian Wheat Board Act, as enacted by this Act [BILL C-4], as well as sections 8 and 20 of the Act itself, being chapter 17 of the Statutes of Canada, 1998, shall COME INTO FORCE.
